LOMBOK:
 need to be installed in a library.so we use pom.mxl
 BROWSER:
  search "lombok maven dependency" in google
  click org.projectlombok >> lombok-Maven Repository
  click latest version on the top left corner
  their wil be maven,gradle,svt,grape..........
  click Mavencopy the code.
 INTELLIJ:
  pom.xml
  dependencies
  paste
  refresh maven(not necessary do if required)-present in right top

  maven->plugins and dependencies present(lombok will be present in dependencies)
  settings->plugins->search->lombok->install

SHORTCUT KEYS:

Alt + Enter
  When we see an error in our code, if we place the cursor on the error and press Alt+Enter we get a list of suggested fixes for the problem.
F2
  to jump next error or warnings.
debug:
  add breakpoint
  right click ->debug->press function plus f7 or f8
ctrl+?
  single line comment for block(multiple line)
alt+ctrl+l
  proper allignment
shift+alt+ctrl+l
  realignment

  
